@CreditFlow.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5246
@ApplicationId = replace-with-application-id

### Health
GET {{CreditFlow.Api_HostAddress}}/health

### OpenAPI JSON
GET {{CreditFlow.Api_HostAddress}}/openapi/v1.json

### Submit application
POST {{CreditFlow.Api_HostAddress}}/applications
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: corr_http_demo_001

{
  "ownerUserId": "local-user-001",
  "borrower": {
    "legalName": "Demo Coffee Imports Ltd",
    "taxId": "DEMO-0001",
    "industry": "Wholesale",
    "monthsInBusiness": 48
  },
  "requestedAmount": 80000,
  "monthlyRevenue": 65000,
  "currency": "USD"
}

### List applications
GET {{CreditFlow.Api_HostAddress}}/applications

### Get application
GET {{CreditFlow.Api_HostAddress}}/applications/{{ApplicationId}}

### Complete KYC - verified
POST {{CreditFlow.Api_HostAddress}}/internal/kyc/applications/{{ApplicationId}}/complete
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: corr_http_demo_001

{
  "matchesSanctionList": false,
  "missingDocuments": false
}

### Complete credit assessment
POST {{CreditFlow.Api_HostAddress}}/internal/credit/applications/{{ApplicationId}}/assess
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: corr_http_demo_001

{
  "assessmentId": null
}

### Upsert credit profile and complete decision
POST {{CreditFlow.Api_HostAddress}}/internal/credit/applications/{{ApplicationId}}/profiles/upsert
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: corr_http_demo_001

{}

### Timeline
GET {{CreditFlow.Api_HostAddress}}/applications/{{ApplicationId}}/timeline

### Decision
GET {{CreditFlow.Api_HostAddress}}/applications/{{ApplicationId}}/decision
